{"tid":2188991,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[絲打入]男奴調教討論區","createTime":"2020-09-04T14:47:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T15:27:15.000Z","uid":96525,"like":6,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"43eb62441f5357b72b65222d49939b73790cdcbd","tid":2188991,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:47:52.000Z","msg":"為免衝擊心靈有棍請上一頁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位S女鍾意點樣調教自己隻奴？<br />\n我最鍾意啲心靈脆弱嘅男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />容易啲調教<br />\n會設立賞罰制度去控制佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n然後佢就會為咗得到你嘅賞賜/稱讚去乖乖聽命令<br />\n耐下佢就會不自覺改變價值觀為咗迎合你<br />\n會讚會錫<br />\n亦都會打會鬧<br />\n玩個陣一定要有safe word<br />\n過程要建立喺雙方安全之上<br />\n平時都係玩下掌摑皮鞭著女裝化妝扮狗仔呢啲普通嘢<br />\n有無人仲有咩玩法/令隻奴更加聽話嘅方法分享下呀？"},{"pid":"accdde00fc86fa78a3033615feabaf567a1da4f9","tid":2188991,"uid":182127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c184d770abdc0f68bfcc2f9dabf38f7e5a801fcb","tid":2188991,"uid":48631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:50:30.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"114b0ac7aaa1a0a6fb5ce6897e5a34dea88ca78e","tid":2188991,"uid":175659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"Gold shower &gt; golden shower"},{"pid":"bea586859ff29b65a8c096a51267405ca55edc0c","tid":2188991,"uid":127929,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T14:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c81dd29